<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>P. Knudsen</author>
<hymn_number>796</hymn_number>
<title>Henoy izany hira vao FFPM796</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Henoy izany hira vao
 Erý an-danitra,
 Fa teraka Jesosinao,
 Ka mahafinaritra.

[V2]
 Ianaronao matetika
 Ny fitiavany,
 Fa sambatra sy tretrika
 Izay sakaizany.

[V3]
 Atero zava-manitra
 Sy volamenam-po
 Ilay Mpanjakan-danitra,
 Mpanjakantsika koa.

[V4]
 Valio fitiavana
 Ilay Zoky tia anao,
 Ateronao fisaorana,
 Derao fa Tomponao.</lyrics>
</song>